Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:04.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Crab Cactus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A cactus which blooms in winter, found in the highlands of South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:15.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)\blur2}What secrets does this cactus hold today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.00,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}With long-standing emotions in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.51,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}mark 20 years with a strong flap of your wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:22.12,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A pretty woman who is looking for a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.25,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sad memories looked back upon with love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.83,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:27.70,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.23,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
