Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Noriko Okaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:24.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you could find the address
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of a man named Tsuyoshi Kitagawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:31.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my asking, but how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:36.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him in early June, during a trip to Shinshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:41.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think much of him at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:45.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but lately I've wanted to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:51.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! You've fallen in love with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:01.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just a simple search. No need for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:08.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Why's she so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any clues or leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and a quick sketch of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's quite the unique individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This sketch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.80,0:03:38.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a cinch! I can use his license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.68,Dialogue,,0004,0004,0006,,{\fad(375,375)\a3\fs28\fnTimes New Roman\bord1.5\shad0}As of 2016, addresses cannot be obtained this way due to changes in the law.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0067,,to get his address from the transportation office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:47.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she really likes him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that when you draw someone's picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:56.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings for that person go into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her drawing doesn't look very—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go do your homework\Nand mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. You shouldn't get in the way of—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko Okaya-{\i1}san{\i0}, lives at—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:22.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I already saw what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A handkerchief. Is it hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:36.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Let's see. 3-9-8... Sumire Lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for bringing me my handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Want some cocoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a nice apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to work at a business firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got sick. I'm recuperating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:12.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I don't see any gas heaters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Self-defense spray...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Huh? What's that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's dated May 19th...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Is a girl's apartment that rare for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until he dumped me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I'm looking for a new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:53.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That man in the sketch sure seems... different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking things might go smoother with a different type of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:05.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I didn't learn much about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:09.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh, well. I guess I'll wait around for the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:14.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But will he really find him that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.50,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(425,0)}One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the aquarium in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither! I hope I can pet the dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably won't rain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The old man's working again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:41.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This Kitagawa guy moved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}without giving his new address to the transportation office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This is gonna take awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I thought it was strange she hired a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}when she already had his license plate number...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So that's what this really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But why does she look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I just remembered I gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers and mourning clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's visiting a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I wonder whose grave it is. It still looks new.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:55.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe it's been six months already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:55.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:04.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, all I did was help with your rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:11.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we have coffee somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:15.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I need to hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then let me drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose grave is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was that lady's boyfriend's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:46.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. He was both my friend and her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fiancé? When did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Yamaguchi Family Grave"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Early June.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}June?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:57.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No doubt about it! It was the guy in the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:00.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This was my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}until he dumped me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} lied about being dumped
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}when her boyfriend was actually dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:11.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two were driving through Utsukushi Highland in Shinshu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when they drove into a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:28.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Pardon my asking, but how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:33.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I met him in early June, during a trip to Shinshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What does it mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Did she meet him when her fiancé caused the accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard the name\NTsuyoshi Kitagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He drives a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A red sports car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! It has to do with that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}?! W-Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:14.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the famous Detective Mouri\Nwould have an assistant like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:19.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It was the only way to get you to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:25.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give any details, but could you start
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:28.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by giving me the name of Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Tatsuo Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He worked at the same company as she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:39.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, you seemed surprised when I mentioned a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:46.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her talking to the police\Nafter the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A red sports car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.01,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yes. There was a young couple in it, chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.38,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We tried to lose them, but then—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:59.98,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We did find two sets of tire tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.34,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.94,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They were just harassing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:08.34,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}At first they kept honking their horn from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.77,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and when we let them go ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.99,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}they swerved right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:17.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It was their fault! Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0} tried to avoid them, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.19,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.70,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Alright. We're looking into the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:26.28,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but even if we do catch them, they'll probably get off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.04,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:32.76,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Things might've been different had you actually collided,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:37.17,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but as they are now, this would be deemed Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.26,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He was speeding, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:45.05,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Do you remember the car's model\Nor license plate number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.06,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Okaya-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:57.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she answered clearly with\N"I don't remember."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was really hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:07.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't describe the couple very well either,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and with no other leads, the police investigation ended after only a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So those clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yes. His license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and a quick sketch of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.51,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh! He's quite the unique individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:30.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} remembered\Nhis plate number and his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Does the fact that she didn't tell the police
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:37.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,125)\blur2}mean that she's going\Nto take matters into her own hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:46.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}! What was the rehabilitation you and Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} talked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:51.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the doctor in charge of her rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she seem at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She worked extremely hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:03.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What normally takes half a year,\Nshe did in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:12.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Her lust for revenge inspired her\Nto get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Let's go see Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I have to somehow change Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}before the old man finds this Kitagawa guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But how—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry! That's a Crab Cactus needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've gotten there when I recently
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,took one to a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:46.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Crab Cactus? Was it Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He liked raising cactuses, even though he was still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:56.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took all of them in after the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone asked for one, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to share them with Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:07.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but that would only remind her of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So she doesn't know I have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:16.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Wait! Crab Cactuses are also known as Christmas Cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What if—!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is your house far from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's on the way to Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stop by there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's odd. There's no telling when the old man will contact her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so she should be at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't tell me he's already found the address?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out the guy's address already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, sure did! Wasn't easy, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wore the bottoms off of my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got off the phone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.83,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But the guy's already living with some chick,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.08,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so I guess she's out of luck—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the address, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:17.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, before that couple gets killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs33\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}katamuite-yuku hizashi ga nagai sakamichi terashite-iru\N{\blur0\c\3c}The last rays of sunlight flow down the long hill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:58.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs33\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kimi wa hitori de hashiru kawaita nodo osaete\N{\blur0\c\3c}You run up it alone, despite your parched throat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:12.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs33\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}motsuresou ni naru ashimoto akirame ga mada osoikakaru\N{\blur0\c\3c}Feeling about to stumble anytime, the desire to give up floods back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:24.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs33\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}yosoku dekinai happening kidou hazureta yume\N{\blur0\c\3c}Events you could never expect have thrown your dream off course
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:38.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs33\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kokoro kowareteku itami no naka\N{\blur0\c\3c}But when your heart's falling apart from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:52.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs33\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}wasurenaide-hoshii koko ni iru-kara\N{\blur0\c\3c}Never forget that I'm always here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.26,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.57,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.97,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:14.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} probably went to the transportation office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}on her own to find Kitagawa's address.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:21.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Unable to find his new address, she hired the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:25.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If she was that intent on rehabilitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:29.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}then there's probably no stopping her\Nfrom wanting vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}How is she planning to get revenge, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:38.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} die instantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:43.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He was still alive after he smashed into the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Burned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:51.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The car's gasoline ignited before he could be pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Aha! That wasn't kerosene at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It was probably gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That accident wasn't our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:50.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your excuses; you're both going to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:51.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are human scum! Get ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to suffer exactly like my boyfriend did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the crazy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:15.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the only way to calm her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:47.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}! Stop this foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this won't bring Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:01.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that! But this is all I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:06.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! Light it on fire and you'll be injured too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:12.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no future now that Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0} is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do is make these people pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:25.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This Crab Cactus sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They bloom in the winter, so in some countries
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they're given as Christmas presents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and even referred to as Christmas Cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:49.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}'s Crab Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I took in all of his cactuses as mementos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi may have died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he lives on in each one of these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:17.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've come!\NThe aquarium was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of us fed the dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:23.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0} slipped and fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The aquarium guy took a picture\Nat that exact moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:30.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:37.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:41.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Boy, am I glad I didn't go!
